*gnugadu-2.0.1 (25 Apr 2004)

  25 Apr 2004; Michal Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> +gnugadu-2.0.1.ebuild,
  gnugadu-2.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  07 Apr 2004; Michal Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> gnugadu-2.0.ebuild:
  Dropping gtkspell support because gnugadu works only with gtkspell-2.0.2.

*gnugadu-2.0 (04 Apr 2004)

  04 Apr 2004; Michal Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> gnugadu-2.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  17 Mar 2004; Michal Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> gnugadu-2.0_pre8.ebuild:
  Added full spell-checking support, thanks to MadeJ <madej@afn.no-ip.org>
  for his comments on gtkspell.

  17 Mar 2004; Michal Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org> gnugadu-2.0_pre8.ebuild:
  Fixed Perl support, added preliminary support for gtkspell.

*gnugadu-2.0_pre8 (17 Mar 2004)

